---
const models = [
  "SaaS subscriptions",
  "Professional trader plans",
  "Enterprise licensing",
  "Data services",
  "Strategy marketplace",
  "AI analysis add-ons",
  "Broker or institutional partnerships",
  "Compliance-dependent future performance-based models"
];
---

<section class="section commercial-section" id="commercial">
  <div class="container commercial-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Commercial model</p>
      <h2>Potential monetization paths</h2>
      <p>
        The platform can support multiple business models over time without depending on profitability claims.
        Every regulated commercial activity must be reviewed with qualified legal and compliance advisors.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="model-list">
      {models.map((model) => <span>{model}</span>)}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <p class="notice">
      Performance fees, managed accounts, copy trading, signal subscriptions, or broker fee-sharing may require
      legal, regulatory, or licensed partner review.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
